<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<RelativeLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    android:orientation="vertical" android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="match_parent"
    android:weightSum="1"
    android:background="#fbfdfd">

<ScrollView xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    android:id="@+id/ScrollView01"
    android:layout_width="fill_parent"
    android:layout_height="fill_parent"
    android:fillViewport="false">

    <RelativeLayout
        android:id="@+id/RelativeLayout01"
        android:layout_width="fill_parent"
        android:layout_height="fill_parent">
        <ImageView
            android:layout_width="50dp"
            android:layout_height="50dp"
            android:src="@drawable/ic_keyboard_arrow_left_black_24dp"
            android:layout_toStartOf="@+id/tvF1"
            android:id="@+id/imageView2"
            android:layout_alignParentTop="true" />
        <ImageView
            android:layout_width="50dp"
            android:layout_height="50dp"
            android:src="@drawable/ic_keyboard_arrow_right_black_24dp"
            android:id="@+id/imageView3"
            android:layout_alignParentTop="true"
            android:layout_alignEnd="@+id/tv3" />
        <TextView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:text="MAN TASK"
            android:textSize="24dp"
            android:textStyle="bold"
            android:gravity="center"
            android:layout_marginLeft="20dp"
            android:layout_marginTop="60dp"
            android:id="@+id/tv2"
            android:layout_alignParentStart="true" />
        <TextView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:text="1. As the game starts, the manual bot has to pick people and secure them by transferring to conveyor assembly help them to get out of castle."
            android:textSize="16dp"
            android:layout_marginLeft="25dp"
            android:layout_marginTop="5dp"
            android:id="@+id/tv3"
            android:layout_below="@+id/tv2"
            android:layout_centerHorizontal="true" />
        <TextView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:layout_marginTop="5dp"
            android:text="2. There will be a king, some Courtier and common people which are trapped in a castle arena."
            android:textSize="16dp"
            android:layout_marginLeft="25dp"
            android:id="@+id/tv4"
            android:layout_below="@+id/tv3"
            android:layout_centerHorizontal="true" />
        <TextView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:layout_marginTop="5dp"
            android:text="3. Aim of bot is to save maximum people trapped in an arena."
            android:textSize="16dp"
            android:layout_marginLeft="25dp"
            android:id="@+id/tv5"
            android:layout_below="@+id/tv4"
            android:layout_centerHorizontal="true" />



        <TextView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:text="GAME FIELD AND OBJECTS: DESCRIPTION"
            android:textSize="24dp"
            android:textStyle="bold"

            android:layout_marginLeft="20dp"
            android:layout_marginTop="20dp"
            android:id="@+id/tv6"
            android:layout_below="@+id/tv5"
            android:layout_alignParentStart="true" />
        <TextView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:text="1. The field consists of an area having the dimension of 3000mm x 2500mm and surrounded by a wooden fence with a height of 100mm."

            android:textSize="16dp"
            android:layout_marginLeft="25dp"
            android:id="@+id/tv7"
            android:layout_marginTop="5dp"
            android:layout_below="@+id/tv6"
            android:layout_centerHorizontal="true" />
        <TextView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:text="2. The common people will be of size 50x50x50mm having hooks on them and Courtier will be of size 60x60x60mm and king will be of size 80x80x80mm."
            android:textSize="16dp"
            android:layout_marginLeft="25dp"
            android:id="@+id/tv8"
            android:layout_marginTop="5dp"
            android:layout_below="@+id/tv7"
            android:layout_centerHorizontal="true" />
        <TextView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:text="3. There are three points, point ‘START’ for manual bot to start and other two points for safe pit where conveyor is fixed."
            android:textSize="16dp"
            android:layout_marginLeft="25dp"
            android:id="@+id/tv9"
            android:layout_marginTop="5dp"
            android:layout_below="@+id/tv8"
            android:layout_centerHorizontal="true" />
        <TextView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:text="4.One conveyor will be for common people and other for Courtier and king both situated at opposite corners "
            android:textSize="16dp"
            android:layout_marginTop="5dp"
            android:layout_marginLeft="25dp"
            android:id="@+id/tv10"
            android:layout_below="@+id/tv9"
            android:layout_centerHorizontal="true" />
        <TextView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:text="5.Safe pits will be of 100x100mm (lxb). . "
            android:textSize="16dp"
            android:layout_marginTop="5dp"
            android:id="@+id/tv11"
            android:layout_below="@+id/tv10"
            android:layout_alignStart="@+id/tv12" />
        <TextView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:text="6. At maximum there will be 5 Courtier and 10 common people and one king in the arena."
            android:textSize="16dp"
            android:layout_marginTop="5dp"
            android:layout_marginLeft="25dp"
            android:id="@+id/tv12"
            android:layout_below="@+id/tv11"
            android:layout_centerHorizontal="true" />


        <TextView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:text="COMPLETION TASKS"
            android:textSize="24dp"
            android:textStyle="bold"

            android:layout_marginLeft="20dp"
            android:layout_marginTop="20dp"
            android:id="@+id/tv13"
            android:layout_below="@+id/tv12"
            android:layout_alignParentStart="true"/>
        <TextView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:text="1.As the game begins the manual bot, starting from point ‘START’ can now pick the people and start putting them on conveyor assembly. "
            android:textSize="16dp"
            android:layout_marginTop="5dp"
            android:layout_marginLeft="25dp"
            android:id="@+id/tv14"
            android:layout_below="@+id/tv13"
            android:layout_centerHorizontal="true"
            android:textIsSelectable="false" />
        <TextView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:text="2 . After picking up all the people manual bot has to pick the king from where he is trapped."
            android:textSize="16dp"
            android:layout_marginTop="5dp"
            android:layout_marginLeft="25dp"
            android:id="@+id/tv15"
            android:layout_below="@+id/tv14"
            android:layout_centerHorizontal="true" />
        <TextView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:text="3. Meanwhile conveyor assembly will start saving the peoples and transferring them to the safe pits. "
            android:textSize="16dp"
            android:layout_marginTop="5dp"
            android:layout_marginLeft="25dp"
            android:id="@+id/tv16"
            android:layout_below="@+id/tv15"
            android:layout_centerHorizontal="true" />

    </RelativeLayout>
</ScrollView>
</RelativeLayout>
